  - Hover (unselected): `--color-neutral-90` bg, same border, same text + underline
  - Selected: `--color-neutral-20` bg (#313D47), same 1px border (subtle highlight), white text
  - Focus: 2px `#6fcfff` (Blue80) border on whichever chip has keyboard focus
  - Disabled: `opacity: --opacity-level-medium; pointer-events: none` on container
- **Error**: 12px `--color-warning-40` text below chip row, 4px gap (via `gap: 4px` on container)
